Hey @Jess thanks! I'll send you an invite to debug this together on Monday. Meanwhile here's how you may reproduce what I see:

2. start ib locally with `"use_webpacked_local_server": "false"`
3. go to any of those apps: table refiner, annotator, visual refiner , redactor. You'll see a blank page & these errors in the console
